6.st=raw_input("enter the string")
count1=0;
count2=0
for i in st:
    if(i.isupper()):
        count1=count1+1
    elif(i.islower()):
        count2=count2+1
print("count of uppercases%s"%count1)
print("count of lowercases%s"%count2)

enter the string Sudharsan
count of uppercases1
count of lowercases8

8.s=[1,2,3,4,5]
sum=0
for i in s:
    if i%2==0:
        sum=sum+i
print(sum)

the even numbers are 2
the even numbers are 4
the sum of even numbers is 6

